history.content:
Interested in learning about technical sales? Join us Thursday, March 1st, 5 - 6:30 PM at 290 HMMB to hear from representatives of Maxim Integrated.

They will be talking about their work experiences and exciting career opportunities in technical semiconductor sales. In this role, you will have the opportunity to use your problem solving skills in electrical engineering and computer science to support the technical challenges customers are facing while designing new hardware products.


Dinner will be provided! We will be raffling off a Hydro Flask water bottle to participants who fill out our feedback form.

RSVP here!
